coords

Class MyCoords

  • java.lang.Object
    • coords.MyCoords
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Coords_converter

    public class MyCoords
extends java.lang.Object
implements Coords_converter
    This class implemnets Coords_converterand represents a basic coordinate system converter, including: 1. The 3D vector between two lat,lon, alt points 2. Adding a 3D vector in meters to a global point. 3. convert a 3D vector from meters to polar coordinates
    Author:
    Shayke Shok and Omer Edut
